      "description": "Superpowers is a complete software development workflow system for coding agents. It's built on composable skills — reusable technique libraries that trigger automatically to guide TDD, planning, debugging, brainstorming, code review, and more. Skills are the building blocks; agents check for applicable skills before every action.",
